<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NGO Registration System</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            background-color: #121212; 
            color: #f0f0f0; 
            text-align: center; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            height: 100vh; 
        }

        /* Logo Styling */
        .logo {
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            object-fit: contain; /* Ensures the whole logo is visible */
            border-radius: 50%; /* Makes it circular */
            background-color: white; /* Adds white bg in case image is transparent */
            border: 4px solid #ff4d4d; /* Theme border color */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
        }

        h1 { 
            color: #ff4d4d; 
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Adjusted size for longer text */
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
            margin-top: 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000; 
            max-width: 900px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        p { 
            font-size: 1.2rem; 
            color: #aaa; 
            margin-bottom: 40px; 
        }

        .btn-container { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            gap: 20px; 
        }

        .btn { 
            padding: 15px 40px; 
            font-size: 1.2rem; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 30px; 
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; 
            font-weight: bold; 
        }

        .btn-login { 
            background: transparent; 
            border: 2px solid #ff4d4d; 
            color: #ff4d4d; 
        }

        .btn-login:hover { 
            background: #ff4d4d; 
            color: white; 
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff4d4d; 
        }

        .btn-register { 
            background: #ff4d4d; 
            color: white; 
            border: 2px solid #ff4d4d; 
        }

        .btn-register:hover { 
            transform: scale(1.05); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff4d4d; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <img src="/images/nss-logo.jpg" alt="Organization Logo" class="logo">

    <h1>NGO Registration and donation management system</h1>
    
    <p>Empowering lives through your generosity. Join us today.</p>
    
    <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-login">Login</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-register">Start Donating</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>